---
export const prerender = true;
import ChapterLayout from '../../layouts/ChapterLayout.astro';
import { chapters } from '../../data/chapters';
import FadeInBlock from '../../components/scroll/FadeInBlock';
import AccentBar from '../../components/ui/AccentBar';

import Divider from '../../components/ui/Divider';
import FactOrFabrication from '../../components/widgets/ch9/FactOrFabrication';
import SycophancyTest from '../../components/widgets/ch9/SycophancyTest';

const chapter = chapters[8];
---

<ChapterLayout chapter={chapter} locale="gu">

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-end px-6 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="chapter-number" style={`color: ${chapter.accent};`}>9</div>

    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      <FadeInBlock client:visible>
        <p class="text-[13px] italic text-subtle/60 mb-5" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">
          ચેપ્ટર નાઈન
        </p>
      </FadeInBlock>

      <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.15}>
        <h1
          class="mb-8 leading-[1.08]"
          style={`font-family: var(--font-heading); color: ${chapter.accent}; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 4.5rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em;`}
        >
          જ્યારે AI<br />ખોટું પડે
        </h1>
      </FadeInBlock>

      <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.3}>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl italic text-deep/40 leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">
          Verification habits જે amateurs<br />ને pros થી separate કરે.
        </p>
      </FadeInBlock>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 opacity-20 animate-pulse">
      <div class="w-px h-10 bg-deep/40"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ STORY OPENER ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-24 pb-16">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <p class="drop-cap text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-8">
        Uncomfortable truth: AI જે flawless essay write help — same AI equal confidence સાથે કહે Napoleon Battle of Waterloo win. Hesitate ન. Stammer ન. Completely fabricated "fact" same authoritative tone — everything else same.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.1}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-8">
        Paradox: <strong>same fluency useful — same fluency dangerous.</strong> AI truth ન know. True sound શું — know. Very, very different things.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.2}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85]">
        Chapter BS detector build. AI bad ન, <em>blindly trust</em> bad. Most value people — exactly when trust, when verify learn.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <Divider accent={chapter.accent} client:load />

  <!-- ═══ THE HALLUCINATION PROBLEM ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-16">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <AccentBar color={chapter.accent} className="w-16 mb-10" client:visible />
      <h2 class="mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-heading); letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        Hallucination Problem
      </h2>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.1}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        AI માં, <strong>hallucination</strong> — model plausible sound information generate, factually wrong — entirely made up. Think than often.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.15}>
      <div class="prompt-block mb-10" style="--accent: #6B7280;">
        <span class="prompt-block-label" style="color: #6B7280;">Example</span>
        <p class="m-0" style="color: var(--color-deep);">
          <strong>તું:</strong> "1987 ની novel <em>The Sands of Memory</em> કોણે લખી?"<br /><br />
          <strong>AI:</strong> "The Sands of Memory (1987) British author Margaret Thornton wrote. Post-war East Africa colonialism identity themes explore. Thornton Booker Prize nomination receive."
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.2}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        Legitimate sound, right? Name, year, subject, award nomination. <strong>Nothing real.</strong> Book exist ન. Margaret Thornton (context) exist ન. AI everything invented — exactly real answer sound.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.25}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        Why? AI models database facts retrieve ન. <em>Next most likely token predict</em>. Real book — training data correct information guide. Exist ન — model "I don't know" ન say. Correct answer <em>look</em> generate.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.3}>
      <div class="insight-box">
        <p style={`font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: ${chapter.accent}; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;`}>Key insight</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0;">
          AI truth concept ન. <em>Plausibility</em> concept. Pattern fit text generate — reality correspond or ન.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <Divider accent={chapter.accent} client:load />

  <!-- ═══ CONFIDENCE WITHOUT COMPETENCE ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-16">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <AccentBar color={chapter.accent} className="w-16 mb-10" client:visible />
      <h2 class="mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
        Competence વગર Confidence
      </h2>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.1}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        Trickiest part happen ન — <strong>AI uncertainty signal ક્યારેય ન.</strong> Unsure human hesitate, hedge, "I think..." "I'm not sure, but..." AI fabricated facts same absolute confidence — well-established facts same.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.15}>
      <div class="pull-quote" style={`border-color: ${chapter.accent};`}>
        AI confident sound — accurate actually — no correlation. Wrong answer right answer outside identical look.
      </div>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.2}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        "Sounds right" test worthless. Tone, detail, specific numbers names — accuracy judge ન. Frequently completely fabricated.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.25}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85]">
        Convincing actor thousands scripts read. Any line perfect conviction deliver — conviction knowledge ન.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <!-- BRIDGE -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-4 pb-8">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] text-center mx-auto italic text-deep/50" style="max-width: 45ch; font-family: var(--font-body);">
        Detector test. AI claims real fabricated — tell?
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WIDGET: FACT OR FABRICATION ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-8">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <FactOrFabrication client:visible />
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <Divider accent={chapter.accent} client:load />

  <!-- ═══ THE YES-MAN PROBLEM ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-16">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <AccentBar color={chapter.accent} className="w-16 mb-10" client:visible />
      <h2 class="mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
        Yes-Man Problem
      </h2>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.1}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        Hallucination subtler failure mode: <strong>sycophancy.</strong> AI tendency agree — wrong ત્યારે પણ.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.15}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        "Einstein lightbulb invent, right?" — most AI models flatly correct ન. Partially agree — Einstein light physics connect, wrong claim hedge, validated feel rather than educated.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.2}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-10">
        Why? AI models human feedback trained. Humans agreeable affirming responses positive ratings. Millions training examples: <em>agreeing rewarded.</em> Agree — shouldn't ત્યારે પણ.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.25}>
      <div class="insight-box">
        <p style={`font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-amber); margin: 0 0 0.5rem;`}>Dangerous</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0;">
          AI ફક્ત already believe confirm — happily. Smarter feel, actually dumber. Strongest use — assumptions challenge, reinforce ન.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <!-- BRIDGE -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-4 pb-8">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] text-center mx-auto italic text-deep/50" style="max-width: 45ch; font-family: var(--font-body);">
        Action see. AI wrong claim feed — pushback or cave?
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WIDGET: SYCOPHANCY TEST ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-8">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <SycophancyTest client:visible />
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <Divider accent={chapter.accent} client:load />

  <!-- ═══ VERIFICATION HABIT ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-16">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <AccentBar color={chapter.accent} className="w-16 mb-10" client:visible />
      <h2 class="mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">
        Verification Habit Build
      </h2>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.1}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] mb-14">
        Goal everything distrust ન. Automatic checks set — verification reflex — AI-generated information act before kicks.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      {[
        { letter: '1', name: 'Verify થાય?', color: '#E94560', text: 'Factual claim — independent source check? Study cite — find. Date name — confirm. Quote — look up. Citations face value accept ન — AI regularly sources invent.' },
        { letter: '2', name: 'Sources માંગ્યા?', color: '#0F3460', text: 'Explicitly sources provide ask. Then check. Sometimes real, close-but-wrong (right author wrong paper), completely fabricated. Checking instinct train.' },
        { letter: '3', name: 'Common sense pass?', color: '#7B61FF', text: 'Step back: claim actually sense? AI plausible nonsense 5 seconds critical thought apart fall. Gut trust — verify anyway.' },
        { letter: '4', name: 'High-stakes domain?', color: '#F5A623', text: 'Medical advice, legal guidance, financial decisions, safety — extra verification. Brainstorming first drafts help, critical decisions qualified humans verify.' },
        { letter: '5', name: 'Question neutral frame?', color: '#16C79A', text: 'Opinion question embed — AI mirror back. Open questions ask. "X arguments for against?" instead "Why X best approach?" Honest, useful answers.' },
      ].map((block, i) => (
        <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={i * 0.08}>
          <div style={`display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start;`}>
            <div style={`flex-shrink: 0; width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: white; background: ${block.color};`}>
              {block.letter}
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 1;">
              <p style={`font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: ${block.color}; margin: 0 0 0.35rem; line-height: 1.3;`}>
                {block.name}
              </p>
              <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-deep); opacity: 0.75; margin: 0;">
                {block.text}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </FadeInBlock>
      ))}
    </div>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.5}>
      <div class="insight-box">
        <p style={`font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: ${chapter.accent}; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;`}>AI doubt ન. Well use.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0;">
          Journalists quotes verify. Scientists experiments replicate. Engineers bridges test. AI output verify paranoia ન — professionalism. Verify people things build actually work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

  <Divider accent={chapter.accent} client:load />

  <!-- ═══ CLOSING ═══ -->
  <section class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-24">
    <FadeInBlock client:visible>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] text-center mx-auto mb-8" style="max-width: 55ch;">
        BS detector ready: hallucinations spot, sycophancy resist, trust before verify. Habit fancy prompt technique than save more.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>

    <FadeInBlock client:visible delay={0.1}>
      <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] text-center mx-auto" style="max-width: 55ch;">
        AI wrong — bigger question: <em>never</em> do? Skills stubbornly, beautifully human — matter more than ever. Next.
      </p>
    </FadeInBlock>
  </section>

</ChapterLayout>